config.description:
Supabase 项目地址。

① SQL Editor 执行：
create table voice_messages (
  id uuid default gen_random_uuid() primary key,
  sender text not null,
  sender_name text not null,
  text_content text not null,
  audio_url text,
  created_at timestamptz default now()
);
alter table voice_messages enable row level security;
create policy "allow_all" on voice_messages for all using (true) with check (true);
create policy "voice_audio_insert" on storage.objects for insert with check (bucket_id = 'voice-audio');
create policy "voice_audio_select" on storage.objects for select using (bucket_id = 'voice-audio');
create policy "voice_audio_update" on storage.objects for update using (bucket_id = 'voice-audio');

② Storage → 新建 bucket，名称填 voice-audio，设为 Public。
